WEBVTT

00:03.445 --> 00:06.581
Soaring 4,000 feet above the Colorado River,...

00:06.859 --> 00:09.844
...the Grand Canyon Skywalk is a modern marvel...

00:10.045 --> 00:15.199
...that offers visitors breathtaking views of this awe-inspiring natural wonder.

00:18.909 --> 00:21.866
Showcasing the canyon in all of its rugged majesty,...

00:22.087 --> 00:26.764
...this one of a kind glass-bottom bridge is an experience like no other.

00:29.138 --> 00:33.902
The U-shaped observation deck stretches 70 feet beyond the canyon's rim.

00:34.383 --> 00:38.691
Though it appears to be floating on air, the structure is rock-solid.

